org.osmdroid.util

Class ResourceProxyImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osmdroid.DefaultResourceProxyImpl
      • org.osmdroid.util.ResourceProxyImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResourceProxy, MapViewConstants

    public class ResourceProxyImpl
extends DefaultResourceProxyImpl
    This is an extension of DefaultResourceProxyImpl that first tries to get from resources by using reflection to get the id of the resource from the package that the context is in.
